    811 MONITOR Displacement or External Loads Monitor Point Definition Main Index Record 3 - TRAILER Word Name Type Description 1 NUMMPT I Number of Monitor Points; e.g., Number of Records 2 MXRECL I Maximum number of words in Monitor Points records; MONSUM records are excluded 3 IMESH I Mesh type: = 0 for structural mesh; = 1 for aerodynamic mesh 4 NMDOFS I T otal number of Monitor Points Component Axes for all Monitor Points 5 ICLASS I CLASS type: = 0 for MONPNT1 (COEF , HM, GNRL); = 1 for DISP; = 2 for MONPNT3 6 NMSUM I Number of MONSUM Entries appended following NUMMPT records Note: 1. The DISP class is used for MONDSP monitor points 4. The STRP class is used for MONCNCM monitor points, which are a variation of aerodynamic MONPNT1’s.
